Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancelot呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  什么都想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 19
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}神之岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是别的岛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,湿度和气温和式根岛没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不是离开很远的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通讯器不见了没有通讯手段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先还是确保水源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以备不时之需的好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那件衣服是  黑色骑士团的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲·修坦菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别用那个名字叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:02:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是红月卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是黑色骑士团的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到了现在也不想隐瞒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  红月卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,罪名是对布里塔尼亚的反叛罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要和扇他们取得联系很困难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是比假装成平民向布里塔尼亚求救要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不知道发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等发觉时已经漂来到这个岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  你不是也遇难了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是活该
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等我的同伴来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,变成俘虏的就会是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO会来救你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么在此之前告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己去确认吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  你也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你设计我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比隐瞒身份要好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会服从ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说呢  自己去想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是鲁路修吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有和任何人说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  在向我开枪以前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\rSTAFF}探索雷达部队从D区向A区移动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找出来  无论如何都要把由菲米娅殿下找到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,花瓶副总督本来乖乖地待着就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事要是被科奈莉娅殿下知道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  没想到会是浮游航空舰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有说过如果这东西实用化的话就让我测试数据吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你制造出来的东西都很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以忍不住实用化了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,强粒子炮也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要试一试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直想见你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塞希尔·格雷米小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,修耐泽尔殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然俯视第二皇子殿下  实在是太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴托雷将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是修耐泽尔·El·布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  借手一用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是变得忠心呢  将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:06:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大人救了本来应该已经被塞到地底深处的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着想得那么死板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的事也全是靠你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛维斯时候的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要道谢的应该是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的主君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴托雷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  塞希尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你在基地等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,琐事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便找一下朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用这艘Avalon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是难得的部件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是看到他昨天的活跃之后就更这么认为了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的命令是殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请自重  再深入就会被追究不敬罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  塞希尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,强粒子炮也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种情况下不能忘记的是优先顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  如果造成混乱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他也可能会获救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是赌在他这上面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为由菲的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特派的重要驾驶员枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我为我的无礼而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意接受任何处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,错的是无法保护部下的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从什么时候发觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,饭店劫持事件那时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候一下子说的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是刚才才得到确信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  我也是太天真了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  为什么没有和科奈莉娅商量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐才不会听我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让她更伤心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  身体还没有恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定憎恨着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于我母亲被杀的事你知道什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是姐姐好像做了挺多的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽安娜王妃是姐姐仰慕的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能问一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  现在在这里的是你熟悉的鲁路修  由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安心下来肚子就饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从粪便和足迹可以知道这里是野生动物经常走的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是设置陷阱的大好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挺熟练的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要试一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能协力确保粮食的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就解开你的拘束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想卖人情的话我是不会上当的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和在学校的时候真是大不相同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算用杠杆…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来做体力劳动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,系统是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去找一下水果之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小心一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌战舰已经通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在空中飞的战舰  别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然继续停留在这片海域很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  还是应该停留在这里继续寻找ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在的情况无法派出搜索队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易靠拉克夏塔才藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还不能确定ZERO和卡莲是否还生存着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一步走错就会关系到组织的存亡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正相反
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有ZERO才有我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是有ZERO才有了组织
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有人才能形成组织
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的思想真是很布里塔尼亚化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里汇集了各种各样的主义主张的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这些人能够统合起来到底是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不正是因为出现了成果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而拿出这个成果的人是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我承认这个结果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这不能和全体人员的生命相比
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候  一个人的生命比众多人民的还要重要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为原军人的话这应该是常识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在这里说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没空听你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是确定情报
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是预言者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个我不是跟你说过去做KnightMare的练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个大傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大傻子?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好久没有向着我用这种口气说话的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啊  装得一副了不起的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为你是ZERO的情人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说过不是的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只会想到下流事情的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说的是你别冲着干部无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跑题了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在布里塔尼亚警戒网的外面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在安全的海域做最大范围的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要定一个时间限制的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只好这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为你的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我要和那种无聊男人对话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲也很有趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兴趣真差
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自认为是观察者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想明天一定会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个落坑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是你的原形吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  有什么怨言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  比起在学校更有活力更有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,脱离骑士团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的话还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为恐怖分子被抓到  结局会很悲惨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想怎么装得这么轻松  原来这才是本意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不凑巧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是ZERO的亲卫队队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也用KnightMare和你战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个红色的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕同归于尽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天也要解决掉你的白壳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲的做法是没有未来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你的未来是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是作为支配体制的一条狗而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名誉布里塔尼亚人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第三公主的骑士大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的武士  枢木玄武的名字在哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不同  要把这个错误的世界改变给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然…如果不这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥是无法安息的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了胜利而不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲不是自杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用这双手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,星星还是没有变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是和那时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和以前大家一起仰望的星空一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能一直那样的话  会是多么的美好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不能回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  如果能够回到过去该多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO和我的父亲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,认为自己是世界的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此明知会使许多无辜的人牺牲…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.99,0:14:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你说要接受现状吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样是和平吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是还有比生命更重要的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有打算放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用错误的方法得到的结果会留下什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有无尽的空虚和悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我哥哥活着的意义是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是错也好对也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这些又是谁决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:14:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了自己能够活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不像样的向上挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找寻着根本看不到的生存意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真丑陋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果枢木还活着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该会在这个神根岛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天早上会派出搜索队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这就是上次说的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  在发掘途中发生了新宿事件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然克洛维斯还是比较适合做这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的看到那个亮光了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  应该是搜索队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确认之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再决定对策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对策
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,思考阶梯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我对这个不太在行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是带『超』这种字眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你太无礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这和我的专长差太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道还不如一开始就拜托塞希尔好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别那么不情愿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲大人也对这样的东西相当执著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吧  巴托雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上还发现了好几处同样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我所发现的这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的地方都被天领化了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\an8}[天领:布里塔尼亚皇帝的直属领地]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只是我的猜测
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对各国的侵攻计划都是以此为中心而实行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后为了解析这里的神秘现象\N还要用到Gawain的Druid系统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\an8}[Gawain：亚瑟王的圆桌武士中之一]\N[Druid：德鲁伊特  古代高卢和英国克尔特人信仰的古代宗教中的祭司阶层]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是没有调整的试作机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才把你叫来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该在这一带的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搜索队如果在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的时间就结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我这样靠不住的骑士在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:16:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连饭都没得吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真正的骑士应该是他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么选择名誉布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那两个人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不许动  她是我的俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里配合我说的去做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的部下放了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是人质交换
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你又这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想说我卑鄙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论付出多少牺牲  都要排除恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要坚持你的规则而舍弃主人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种表情  看来你的规则已经被打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:17:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一个被当成人偶的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明一个人就什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀  你不用管我  去战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.13,0:18:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个石头脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请退后  我的主君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木少校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅殿下也在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,捕获  快抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO  那里有KnightMare
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  就用那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没人  而且启动着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人墙  在由菲米娅殿下前做人墙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  这台KnightMare
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是走运
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,修耐泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  Gawain被
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抢回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这台机体不能交给ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,修耐泽尔  现在还…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一级警报  一级警报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,洞口有Sutherland
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧了  就这么冲出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,武器还是未完成的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO  敌方有援军
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个启动着的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightMare在空中…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gawain被
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的Gawain被…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  只不过是实验机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是为两人的无事而庆祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,修耐泽尔哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲  很抱歉来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下  那么按照预定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木朱雀少校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以违反第二级军纪的嫌疑逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我的骑士  这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下再想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之现在先…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和扇联络上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样在外洋和部队合流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  还有就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲二式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:20:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经回收了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了向朝比奈和千叶道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有对你是不想使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木少校  服从命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了  谁管你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一定要活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道你是怎么从Lancelot里出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把能够消灭ZERO的千载难逢的机会给浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保住自己的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有什么想要抗辩的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比这个更确实的违反命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,详细情况还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  才刚完成石川的镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.36,0:21:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:21:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九州地区的关门大桥被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其他还有四处的陆路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.39,0:22:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以及近海有大量的强袭登陆艇接近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.01,0:22:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是中华联邦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没有宣战布告啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那些船体上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.86,0:22:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有日本的国旗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,修耐泽尔为什么会在那个岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.85,0:23:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个地方藏着什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.47,0:23:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时还能相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.78,0:24:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还要考虑卡莲和朱雀的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.55,0:24:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  现在对应九州的事才是关键
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.22,0:24:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是决定黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我自己的将来
